<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: ball lightning -->
  <VPE_BallLightning.label>球状闪电</VPE_BallLightning.label>
  <!-- EN: The caster compresses a ball of condensed electricity which will slowly move to a designated location. A few seconds after release, it will start discharging into nearby surrounding targets with living bolts of electricity. -->
  <VPE_BallLightning.description>施放者将电流压缩成致密的球状，并将其缓慢送出。送出几秒后，球状闪电会开始放电，持续电击周围的目标</VPE_BallLightning.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_BallLightning.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_BallLightning.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 球状闪电 -->
  <VPE_BallLightning.verbProperties.label>球状闪电</VPE_BallLightning.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: bolt -->
  <VPE_Bolt.label>闪电</VPE_Bolt.label>
  <!-- EN: Hurls a weak bolt of electricity to strike a small target, inflicting minor burns on direct hits and area EMP damage. -->
  <VPE_Bolt.description>将一束微弱的闪电射向目标，造成少量的烧伤和范围攻击的EMP伤害。</VPE_Bolt.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_Bolt.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_Bolt.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 闪电 -->
  <VPE_Bolt.verbProperties.label>闪电</VPE_Bolt.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: chain bolt -->
  <VPE_ChainBolt.label>链式闪电</VPE_ChainBolt.label>
  <!-- EN: Projects a living bolt of electricity to a target which can then follow up with 5 more nearby targets, inflicting small burns and EMP damage. -->
  <VPE_ChainBolt.description>将一束活跃的闪电射向目标，随后它会持续跳跃向最多5个周围的目标，造成少量的烧伤和EMP伤害。</VPE_ChainBolt.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_ChainBolt.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_ChainBolt.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 链式闪电 -->
  <VPE_ChainBolt.verbProperties.label>链式闪电</VPE_ChainBolt.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: flashstorm -->
  <VPE_Flashstorm.label>闪电风暴</VPE_Flashstorm.label>
  <!-- EN: Use concentrated differential-pressure skipgates in the atmosphere to generate a localized flashstorm. The storm will strike the area with lightning for some time before dissipating. -->
  <VPE_Flashstorm.description>在大气层里打开集中的压差折跃门，生成一片覆盖一定区域的闪电风暴。风暴会持续轰击目标区域，直至自己消散。</VPE_Flashstorm.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_Flashstorm.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_Flashstorm.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 闪电风暴 -->
  <VPE_Flashstorm.verbProperties.label>闪电风暴</VPE_Flashstorm.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: hurricane -->
  <VPE_Hurricane.label>骤雨飓风</VPE_Hurricane.label>
  <!-- EN: The caster forcibly changes the weather - using widespread differential-pressure skipgates - to a downpour with hurricane-force winds, which lasts as long as the caster can manage the heat accumulation and can instantly stop at-will. Those outdoors will experience progressively severe limitations to sight, moving and manipulation to the point they come to a complete stop. -->
  <VPE_Hurricane.description>施放者使用大量分散的压差折跃门扭曲天气，造成倾盆大雨和强力的飓风,只要能够承受心灵熵就可以不断维持。户外人的视力，移动能力和操作能力会逐渐被限制，直到完全停滞。</VPE_Hurricane.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_Hurricane.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_Hurricane.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 暴风骤雨 -->
  <VPE_Hurricane.verbProperties.label>骤雨飓风</VPE_Hurricane.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: recharge -->
  <VPE_Recharge.label>电力充能</VPE_Recharge.label>
  <!-- EN: Carefully and delicately tunes a stream of electricity to a touched battery to charge it with 100kW or the equivalent of 100 Wd/s. The duration of charge depends on the caster’s psychic sensitivity. -->
  <VPE_Recharge.description>将一束精心调制的可用电力送入接触的电池中，充入100kW或是等效100Wd/s的电力。充能的时间取决于施放者的心灵敏感度。</VPE_Recharge.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_Recharge.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_Recharge.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 电力充能 -->
  <VPE_Recharge.verbProperties.label>电力充能</VPE_Recharge.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: static aura -->
  <VPE_StaticAura.label>静电光环</VPE_StaticAura.label>
  <!-- EN: The caster designates a nearby target to receive an aura of surging electricity, which will inflict EMP effects on anything foreign that they approach, including structures, pawns and electrical objects. -->
  <VPE_StaticAura.description>施放者赋予一个附近目标一个充斥着电力的光环，会对所有附近的目标施加EMP伤害，包括建筑，人员和电器。</VPE_StaticAura.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_StaticAura.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_StaticAura.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 静电光环 -->
  <VPE_StaticAura.verbProperties.label>静电光环</VPE_StaticAura.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: static pulse -->
  <VPE_StaticPulse.label>静电脉冲</VPE_StaticPulse.label>
  <!-- EN: The caster dumps a massive amount of voltage into the surrounding air, causing an EMP blast in a huge radius which is otherwise harmless. -->
  <VPE_StaticPulse.description>施放者将大量高压电输入周围的空气，造成大范围的EMP爆炸。</VPE_StaticPulse.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_StaticPulse.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_StaticPulse.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 静电脉冲 -->
  <VPE_StaticPulse.verbProperties.label>静电脉冲</VPE_StaticPulse.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: thunderbolt -->
  <VPE_Thunderbolt.label>雷击</VPE_Thunderbolt.label>
  <!-- EN: Summons a bolt of lightning to strike a target, inflicting burns on direct hits and a larger area EMP damage. -->
  <VPE_Thunderbolt.description>召唤一束闪电攻击目标，造成烧伤和大范围的EMP伤害。</VPE_Thunderbolt.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_Thunderbolt.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_Thunderbolt.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 雷击 -->
  <VPE_Thunderbolt.verbProperties.label>雷击</VPE_Thunderbolt.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: vortex -->
  <VPE_Vortex.label>电力漩涡</VPE_Vortex.label>
  <!-- EN: Manifests a gaping vortex of high-voltage electricity - redirected via skipgate from a nebula storm - at a target area with a large effect. Severely hampers movement and manipulating proportionately, with the strongest effect at the center. -->
  <VPE_Vortex.description>从星云风暴中折跃过来一个暴涨的高压电漩涡。受影响的目标的移动能力和操作能力会严重下降，越靠近中央越甚。</VPE_Vortex.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_Vortex.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_Vortex.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 电力漩涡 -->
  <VPE_Vortex.verbProperties.label>电力漩涡</VPE_Vortex.verbProperties.label>
  
</LanguageData>